an Bulaga]] || UFA || March 10, 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.packersnews.com/story/sports/nfl/packers/insidersblog/2015/03/10/bryan-bulaga-returns-five-year-deal/24704625// |title=Bulaga reportedly signs 5-year, $33.75 million deal |publisher=Packersnews.com |date= |accessdate=2015-03-10}}</ref> || Green Bay Packers\n|-  style=\"background:#CFC; text-align:center;\"\n| NT || [[Letroy Guion]] || UFA || March 30, 2015<ref name=\"packers1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.packersnews.com/story/sports/nfl/packers/insidersblog/2015/03/30/packers-bring-back-dt-letroy-guion/70667036/ |title=Packers give Raji, Guion another chancel |publisher=Packersnews.com |date=2015-03-30 |accessdate=2015-03-30}}</ref>|| Green Bay Packers\n|-  style=\"background:#CFC; text-align:center;\"\n| NT || [[B. J. Raji]] || UFA ||  March 30, 2015<ref name=\"packers1\"/> || Green Bay Packers\n|-  style=\"background:#FCD; text-align:center;\"\n| ILB || [[Jamari Lattimore]] || UFA || April 1, 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/blog/new-york-jets/post/_/id/50344/jets-sign-former-packers-lb-jamari-lattimore-re-sign-lt-ben-ijalana?ex_cid=espnapi_public |title=Jets sign former Packers LB Jamari Lattimore, re-sign LT Ben Ijalana |publisher=espn.com |date=2015-04-01 |accessdate=2015-04-01}}</ref> || [[New York Jets]]\n|-  style=\"background:#; text-align:center;\"\n| CB || [[Jarrett Bush]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rotoworld.com/player/nfl/4067/jarrett-bush|title=Report: Jarrett Bush suspended additional 10 games |publisher=rotoworld.com |accessdate=2016-02-22}}</ref> || UFA || || \n|-  style=\"background:#FCD; text-align:center;\"\n| CB || [[Davon House]] || UFA || March 10, 2015 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000000477655/article/davon-house-to-join-jaguars-at-625m-per-year|title=Report: Davon House to join Jaguars at $6.25M per year |publisher=nfl.com |date= |accessdate=2015-03-10}}</ref> || [[Jacksonville Jaguars]]\n|-  style=\"background:#FCD; text-align:center;\"\n